Nerr SmartTrader - Multi Broker Trader
By Leon Zhuang @Nerrsoft
http://nerrsoft.com

It's a scalping EA (Expert Advisor) for MetaTrader4, use to trade on two or more brokers, check the price with difference broker, if the price difference is big enough (you can set), open order on these brokers at same time, one Buy order one Sell order, then when total profit greater than your target (you can set too) close orders at same time. It can run on any symbol.

=Install=
0. You need two brokers account and you must install MySQL 5.5 first
1. Copy the "experts" forder to both your two broker's MateTrader4 installation folder.
2. Restart your two MateTrader4 terminal.
3. Setup master client - new a chart in one of you MateTrader4, load "nst_mbt_master"
4. Setup slave client - new a chart in one of you MateTrader4, load "nst_mbt_slave"
5. ...


